param_config_text:
# configs/param_config.yaml

parameters:
  # -------------------------
  # Operating conditions
  # -------------------------
  - name: Tfc                 # Cell temperature (K)
    type: continuous
    low: 333
    high: 363
    fixed: false

  - name: Pa_des              # Desired cell pressure (Pa)
    type: continuous
    low: 130000.0
    high: 300000.0
    fixed: false

  - name: Pc_des              # Cathode pressure (Pa) = Pa_des - 20000
    type: continuous
    derived: "Pa_des - 20000"   # computed from Pa_des — no manual edit needed
    fixed: true                  # value is computed at runtime

  - name: Sc                  # Stoichiometry anode
    type: continuous
    low: 1.1
    high: 3.0
    fixed: false

  - name: Sa                  # Stoichiometry cathode 
    type: continuous
    value: 1.3
    fixed: true

  - name: Phi_c_des          # Entrance humidity anode 
    type: continuous
    low: 0.1
    high: 0.7
    fixed: false

  - name: Phi_a_des          # Anode humidity 
    type: continuous
    value: 0.5
    fixed: true

  # -------------------------------------
  # Undetermined physical parameters
  # -------------------------------------
  - name: epsilon_gdl        # GDL porosity
    type: continuous
    low: 0.55
    high: 0.8
    fixed: false

  - name: tau                # Pore structure coefficient
    type: continuous
    low: 1.0
    high: 4.0
    fixed: false

  - name: epsilon_mc         # CL ionomer volume fraction
    type: continuous
    low: 0.15
    high: 0.4
    fixed: false

  - name: epsilon_c          # GDL compression ratio
    type: continuous
    low: 0.15
    high: 0.3
    fixed: false

  - name: e                  # Capillary exponent (discrete!)
    type: integer
    low: 3
    high: 5
    fixed: false
    # We could also try to do {3,4,5} -> switch to categorical
    # type: categorical
    # values: [3, 4, 5]

  - name: Re                 # Electron conduction resistance (Ω·m²)
    type: continuous
    low: 5.0e-7
    high: 5.0e-6
    fixed: false

  - name: i0_c_ref           # Cathode exchange current density (A/m²)
    type: continuous
    low: 0.001
    high: 80
    fixed: false

  - name: kappa_co           # Crossover correction coefficient (mol/(m·s·Pa))
    type: continuous
    low: 15
    high: 40
    fixed: false

  - name: kappa_c            # Overpotential correction exponent
    type: continuous
    low: 0
    high: 2.5
    fixed: false

  - name: a_slim
    type: continuous
    value: 0
    fixed: true

  - name: b_slim
    type: continuous
    value: 1
    fixed: true

  - name: a_switch
    type: continuous
    value: 0.99
    fixed: true
simulator_defaults_text:
# configs/simulator_defaults.yaml

# --- Modes & plotting (match old sampler) ---
type_current: polarization
type_plot: fixed
type_fuel_cell: manual_setup   # <- previously was manual_setup in build_fixed_parameters()

# --- Silence UI/aux during batch runs (match old) ---
type_auxiliary: no_auxiliary
type_control: no_control
type_purge: no_purge
type_display: no_display

# --- How to source helper-derived pieces (match old behavior) ---
override_current_params: false            # do NOT override helper timing by default
override_polarization_timing: false
use_computing_from_helpers: true          # use computing_parameters(...) as before

# Optional manual overrides (only used if flags above say so)
delta_pola: null                          # [delta_t_load_pola, delta_t_break_pola, delta_i_pola, delta_t_ini_pola]
max_step: null
n_gdl: null
t_purge: null                             # [purge_time, delta_purge]

# --- Geometry/constants (old code pulled these from helpers; do NOT override here) ---
# If you want to force any of these, uncomment and set values. Otherwise helpers will supply them.

# Hgdl:
# Hmem:
# Hcl:
# Hgc:
# Wgc:
